      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW CORA (1) finished well back at this track last time when a 12 length fifth (23.66) but scored five back at Warrnambool (26.43). Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Has winning claims on her best figures. JUST ANGELIC (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing eighth (25.16) in a Rank Limit - Grade 5 at Traralgon. Solid record here winning five races. Cannot be taken lightly. JUSTIFIED JIM (6) comes off an average effort last start when sixth at Shepparton over 450m behind Amron Tommy (26.71) in a Grade 5. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings five times from seven starts. Has the ability to give this a shake. ASTUTE QUEEN (4) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
